title: Fix bug in request handling
body:
# Bug

```rs
use ohkami::prelude::*;

#[tokio::main]
async fn main() {
    Ohkami::new(
        "/".GET(|| async {"Hello!"})
    )
}
```

returned `404 Not Found` for request `GET /`.

# Fix

Strip trailing '/' in request path before pass request to router.

This additionally support any request path having trailing slash.
